title: Willows at the University
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Willows at the University', 'Come home to luxury living in Charlotte with the Willows at the University!', 'Our 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments feature private balconies, chef-inspired kitchens, and kitchen islands for entertaining.', 'Designed with the community in mind, our neighborhood houses two pet parks, a resort-style pool, a state-of-the-art fitness center, a theater room, and an outdoor firepit.', 'Located near I-85 and I-485, your commute will be easier than ever, and adventure only a short drive away.', "You'll be just a few minutes away from University North Carolina Charlotte and all the shopping, dining, and entertainment you could wish for.", 'Conveniently placed on the Northeast side of Charlotte, spend weekends exploring the lush greenery of the local parks and greenways or take in the Nascar Racing Experience at Charlotte Motor Speedway.', "Don't hesitate to discover all that can be found right outside your door.", 'The natural world waits at Reedy Creek Park and the Ribbonwalk Nature Preserve.', 'In under an hour you can be hiking in Uwharrie National Forest or visiting a nearby lake.', "Find out what it's like to title: Deep Kitchen Cabinets, Clubroom with Gourmet Coffee Station
posting_body: ['MAKE YOUR WAY TO PROVENZA AT INDIAN TRAIL', 'Go for a morning run at McAlpine Creek Park or take the nearby Andrew Jackson Highway for easy access into uptown Charlotte when you live at Provenza at Indian Trail.', 'This brand-new community in Indian Trail, NC has a wide selection of one, two and three bedroom apartments now available for rent.', 'These homes have a beautiful assortment of features such as walk-in closets, private patios and in-home washers and dryers.', 'Check out all of the wonderful attractions inside and outside this lovely community.', 'Call today and join this brand-new community at Provenza at Indian Trail.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 33', 'OR Text', '33', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1044 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Full-Size Washer and Dryer in Each Home', '- Private Patio/Balcony', '- Garden Tub', '- Walk-in Closet', '- Eat-in Kitchen', '- Deep Kitchen Cabinets', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Community Amenities', '- Apartment Homes Surrounded by Walking Trails with Pond', '- 24-Hour Fitness Center with Towel Service', '- Off Leash Dog Park', '- Computer Lounge', '- Clubroom with Gourmet Coffee Station', '- Swimming Pool & Lounge Deck', '- Gas Grills', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $400 pet fee and $20 monthly pet rent per month.', 'There is no weight limit, but we do have breed restrictions.', 'Anyone with a dog over 75 lbs. will be asked to choose a 1st floor apartment home.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday:1:00PM-5:00PM', 'Provenza at Indian Trail', '1021 Glenn Valley Lane, Indian Trail, NC, 28079', 'v7oAFxndo7C1']

title: No Lease.  Woodspring Suites weekly rates starting at $430.00!
posting_body: ['NO HASSLE - NO CREDIT CHECKS', 'Before you decide to stay at Woodspring Suites, we want you to be prepared--prepared for a better experience.', 'What that means to us is truly affordable, incredibly clean, safer, simple, flexible experience.', 'And this is more than just a nice idea--its the Woodspring Suites promise.', 'So how do we do it?', 'By combining all the convenience of a hotel with all the essentials of a apartment.', "We are a hybrid--and that makes us better than a hotel, an apartment or any other short-term housing accommodations you'll find.", 'Think about it-no extras padded into our price, no hidden fees.', 'No lease to sign, no utilities to set up.', "That's just for starters.", "Find out below more of what to expect when you're here.", 'Clean & Safe--Secure building access with with electronic protected interior.', 'A Safety Attendant available after hours.', 'All rooms are deep-cleaned after each check-out and then go through a vigorous multi-point cleaning.', 'Kitchen--Kitchens have a full-size refrigerator/freezer, a double burner cook-top, large microwave, cabinet space, and a spacious sink.', 'Furnished Studio--Dresser, nightstand,, eating table with chair, clothes hanging rack, and extra storage space.', 'Satellite/Cable--Premium Satellite or Cable television with Movie Channels.', '24 Hour Laundry Service--On site laundry facility with keyed guest access only for your safety', 'Linen Exchange--During office hours bring your towels/linens to the front desk for a quick exchange.', 'High Speed Internet--Go online 24/7 with free wifi.', 'High speed internet available for a nominal fee.', 'Coffeemaker--A drip coffeemaker that makes 6 to 10 cups.', 'Yours to keep with a one time fee.', 'Housekeeping--Housekeeping is included every other week.', 'Additional cleaning can be purchased for a one-time.', 'Dish Pack--Service for two including plates, bowls, mugs, utensils, cooking slotted turner, skillet, saucepan, dish cloth, and kitchen towel.', 'Yours to keep for a one-time.', 'Pets--Dogs are welcome (NO Cats).', '$50.00 fee required at check-in plus $10.00 per night.', 'Service animals always allowed at no cost.']

title: !!Nice 2BR / 2Ba available now Rent: $500
posting_body: ['!!', 'Nice 2BR / 2Ba available now Rent: $700/mo, includes free water@2!', 'We have a friendly atmosphere of diverse tenants.', 'Included within our property is off street parking, an indoor pool, laundry facilities in every building, onsite security, 24hr maintenance, and much more!', 'Our location is perfect!', 'We are within walking distance from major grocery stores, fast food restaurants, sit down restaurants, gas stations and corporate businesses like Sprint, T-Mobile, Sherwin Williams, Frito-Lay and Pizza Hut.', 'We are also right off of Highway I-70 at 3711 SW Park South Court, making traveling easy peasy!', 'Hard wood floors throughout the house.', 'Large basement with Washer dryer.', 'Balcony in the back and a drive way/parking in the back of the house.', 'This is a very comfortable house ideally located, 10 minutes walk to metro, shopping restaurants and cinema and only a few minutes drive to downtown.', 'A quite residential street and neighborhood.', 'Plenty of off street parking.', 'Ideal for a small family, couples, or roommates.', 'Brand new Kitchen appliances, beautiful window views of the neighborhood, laundry mat is provided next door 1 min walking distance.', 'Text me if interested:~(646) 470-58 78\u202c']
